      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 20 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 8 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 21</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You physically age your body by 1 or 2 age categories, changing your appearance and incurring the associated penalties with the new age category.<br><br>This technique lasts until 1d4+1 rounds after your Chakra Pool falls below 10%, or it can be dismissed as any dismissible technique can.</p>\n\n\n\n",
